INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5887','<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center;\">产品简介</span>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">车内空气污染物比室内高</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">10倍，你知道吗？车内空间狭小，PM2.5的含量是室内的5倍多，开车半小时相当室内待半天，在堵车时更严重！汽车甲醛含量是室内的10倍以上，甲醛对于人体的危害总所周知，车内已成为空气健康的重灾区！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">除甲醛四大误区</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">:汽车清新去甲醛，香精与化合物的合成，不能去甲醛，反而会分家甲醛；竹炭去甲醛，效果甚微，吸附能力十分有限；车载净化器，竹炭吸附原理类似，汽车空气净化器较小，吸附能力有限；开窗散味，甲醛无色无味，甲醛释放周期长达十多年，是持久的危害。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">空气说车用空气净化剂快速去除异味喷出健康，拒霾</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 29px;\">&ldquo;千里之外&rdquo;。强效去除汽车甲醛，一分钟解决甲醛，TVOC，烟味，异味。采用最新净化科技，提取自然界净化修复能力超强的有益微生物高效净化，安全无害。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 