INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5929','<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\">产品简介</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">海绵微针是从生活在清洁水域中的多细胞海绵动物体内提取的中空硅质骨针。海绵微针美容疗法是一种自然的生物-物理美容焕肤方法，解决了传统微针仪器带来的疼痛，出血和操作麻烦等问题。海绵微针能渗入表皮层和角质层，72小时持续刺激细胞并促使细胞分裂再生，唤醒皮肤的正常代谢，帮助皮肤排出各种废弃物及毒素，使老化角质层自然脱落，让皮肤在短时间内恢复弹性和健康。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">海绵微针不仅蕴含抗病毒、抗菌以及自我保护性药物，同时也含有大量的活性生物材料，传递有效物质的能力十分显著，在粉刺位、色素沉着等各种皮肤问题上涂抹，不但能促进老化角质脱落、改善肤质；还能抗炎镇静，诱导血液循环，提升皮肤免疫力，让肌肤宛若新生，该产品一经面市，就受到美容行业的追捧。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.xiaobaodt.com/file/upload/201705/31/141804971.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"612\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2em; font-family: \'