zing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1、蔓越莓，又称蔓越橘、小红莓，主要生长在北美寒冷的酸性土壤中。常绿灌木，果实成熟后呈红色浆果状。目前在北美被当做经济作物大量种植，其果实富含丰富的营养价值，有着&ldquo;北美红宝石&rdquo;的美誉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2、蓝莓，又称越桔，起源于北美，多年生灌木小浆果果树。因果实呈蓝色，故称为蓝莓。北美地区的蓝莓质量全球闻名。蓝莓营养丰富，不仅富含常规营养成分，而且还含有极为丰富的黄酮类和多糖类化合物，因此又被称为&ldquo;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">水果皇后&rdquo;和&ldquo;抗氧化之王&rdquo;。在世界卫生组织公布的绿茶等十大健康食品中，蓝莓是唯一入选的水果。联合国粮农组织也将蓝莓列为&ldquo;人类五大健康食品之一&rdquo;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3、樱桃又名车厘子，莺桃，荆桃，楔桃，英桃</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">，樱珠，含桃，玛瑙，樱珠等。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">樱桃全身皆可入药，鲜果具有发汗、益气、祛风、透疹的功效，适用于四肢麻木和风湿性腰腿病的食疗。樱桃性热，味甘，具有益气、健脾、和胃、祛风湿的功效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">4、亚麻籽粉对以下人群有着特殊功效：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-si